data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $4,000 TOWARD BUYERS’ COST/RATE BUY DOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER! Large living area with cathedral ceiling and fireplace with gas logs. Pantry, lots of cabinets/storage and gas stove in kitchen. Master suite bathroom has private water closet. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms, good closets in secondary bedrooms. Roof replaced in 2022. Popular Yukon addition close to desirable elementary school and splash pad. Fantastic price point and opportunity for home ownership in Yukon school district.
